somewhere a few miles from the maxiamals base a strnage wave ripped 
through the air like it was water and out stepped a human by the name 
of Alex and a transformer followed with a few pieces of Equipment on 
a trailer with a light pop the wave disappeared leaving them 2 in a 
field "well looks like it worked so far" rapidspeed said looking 
around at all the plants and animals "ya there no smog in the air or 
craters from past battles" Alex said around with rapid

"Well we better get to work" Alex said looking at a metal 
braclet "computer show us current location of Maxiaml base in this 
time period" alex said 

the braclet started to flash as a 3D map of the world appeared with a 
blinking dot "show current area of Predicon base" he said again as a 
2nd dot appeared 

"well rapid I say we report to the maximal base what u think" alex 
said turning off his computer and looking over at rapid "we sould 
prime gave us order to report to the maxiamls base and not gest 
charge right for the predicons" rapid said looking over at where the 
predicons base would likely be 

"ok then maxiamls base it is then" alex said looking through the 
equipment they brought and pulled out a kind of hook "ok rdy when u 
are Rapid" alex said walking up to rapid 

"there days i hate being a transformer" he said with a laugh as he 
transformed into a motorcycle and let alex hook the trailer to him 
and climb on the motorcycle sit as rapid took off towards the 
maxiamls base quickly
